                    <span>I've been using the I Ching for twenty years and have to say this is the most insightful book I've read on it in that time.  It's ideal for anyone who might have felt put off by the often arcane concepts of the I Ching but would also be very useful for seasoned users who will find Sarah Dening's insights add depth to the traditional text.  It fulfils its title perfectly: an ideal companion for everyday use with the I Ching.</span>
                  
